# Cursor Rules for PhoneGuard AIoT

## 🌐 1. Language Rules
* Always communicate with the user in Vietnamese.
* All comments inside code files (Python, JS, HTML, CSS) must be detailed and written in accented Vietnamese (Tiếng Việt có dấu).

## 🛠️ 2. Debugging & Logs
* Include detailed debug logs in both Backend (Python `logging` or `print`) and Frontend (JS `console.log`). Log key actions such as telemetry receipts, DB inserts, WebSocket broadcasts, and AI evaluations.

## 🎨 3. UI/UX Rules
* Follow the glassmorphic dark tech bento design documented in `docs/design_system_and_skills.md`.

## 🚀 4. Git Automation
* Once a task or code file is finished, add, commit, and push changes to the repository: `https://github.com/Phuc-Bang/phoneguard-aiot.git`.
